data.description: NEW PRICE $1,190,000 - Schedule today to preview!  This 2-storey, 10 feet ceiling, pavered driveway home is on approximately 0.19 acres lot size built in 2016 by D. R. HORTON. The popular KALLAN floor plan spans at a total square feet of 4,372 consisting of 4 (2 en suites) bedrooms, 4.5 baths, screened-in pool and has 3 car tandem garage with ample space for a golf cart. It is simply stunning with luxury vinyl throughout, tastefully decorated and wonderful for entertaining!!   This house is 5.8 miles to Disney and Hamlin Town Center for your groceries, dining and shopping needs.     On the first level is the den which is currently used as an office and may use it as a library or study or even a work-out room. Other areas are the formal dining, storage that can be used as wine cellar as well as additional full and half bathrooms.  A well-equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances, double oven, quality kitchen cabinetry and, large island for preparing meals and providing ease to interact with guests in the living room. The bar area is across from the walk-in built in pantry by the formal dining and kitchen.     The wrought iron railing stairs leads to the second floor of a very spacious loft area (which may be used as theater room or game room) has decorative stoned-wall and an electric fireplace.  The laundry has a washtub/sink as well as full-sized washer and dryer. An en suite primary bedroom has customed built-in closet space while the bathroom is tiled has His and Hers sinks, separate heated hydro tub, separate shower and linen closet. Another en suite remaining while one of the other bedroom is used as a hobby room with closet space as the craft area.      The exterior backyard has screened-in paved pool area with tropical theme with fire bowls and varietals mood lighting which lights up the pool at night surrounded by pristine landscaping. There are solar panels on the roof to conserve energy as well as water filtration system throughout the house - these are all paid for.      To top it all, it is located in premier ommunity offering 2 Clubhouses with Fitness Centers, 3 Community Pools, Tennis Courts, Mini Golf, Walking Trails, Parks, Playgrounds, a Community Dock and so much more!
